import React from "react"

function EmployeeRow(props) {
    return
    <tbody>
        <tr>
        <th>1{props.image}</th>
        <th>2{props.name}</th>
        <th>3{props.phone}</th>
        <th>4{props.email}</th>
        <th>5{props.dob}</th>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
}

export default EmployeeRow;
